	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valde delector prolixis tuis literis, domine colende et frater charissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego vero breves semper scribo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed boni consules, praesertim nunc, quum supra 14 dies decubuerim et etiamnum sim attritis prorsus viribus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuas 1. iulii scriptas accepi et cum fratribus communicavi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De rebus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallicarum</placeName> ecclesiarum semper avemus audire felicia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non infelicia scripsisti; feliciora expectamus, quinimo oramus dominum, ut is nobis adsit et adversariorum cruenta infringat consilia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mihi quidem perplaceret, si tu ex libris d. <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Petri Martyris</persName> colligeres locos communes et quidem breves et ordine didactico compositos; si quis alius hoc praestare poterit, tu poteris inprimis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non puto iure posse conqueri typographos nostros, quum hoc videatur novum fore opus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsit d. <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyr</persName> elegantissimos commentarios in libros Regum, quos excudet brevi d. <persName ref="p1227" cert="high">Froschouerus</persName>; utiles erunt hi inprimis ad hoc tuum institutum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed primo quidem commentarios in 3 Reg. arbitror edendos, deinde quod restat in 4. librum; postremo adiicientur illis commentarii in libros Samuelis; nunc ecuduntur commentarii in Ethica <persName ref="p18432" cert="high">Aristotelis</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expecto summo cum desiderio, quod scribes de rebus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallicis</placeName> et bello illo <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglicano</placeName>, pacatumne sit an duret.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Video mira texi a <persName type="citizen_name">pontifice Romano</persName> et suis consiliariis; cuperem ergo bella illa <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglica</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825" cert="high">Danica</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2520" cert="high">Svedica</placeName> esse pacata.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Orabimus dominum, ut is ecclesiae suae adsit et adversariorum consilia cruenta dissipet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Commendo tibi hos studiosos <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonos</placeName>; alter <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2406" cert="high">Wenceslaus Ostrorog</persName>, viri maximi in <placeName ref="l2472" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Polonia</placeName> et piissimi, filius est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta d. <persName ref="p4791" cert="high">Crispinum</persName>, d. <persName ref="p4227" cert="high">Badium</persName> et alios viros bonos; nostri omnes te salutant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 26. iulii anno 1563.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Theodoro Bezae</persName>, fidelissimo <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro, domino colendo et fratri charissimo meo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genff</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
